British actor Idris Elba and his wife Sabrina say Mama Oliech is their best place to visit in Africa. The couple told Ebony magazine January issue that Mama Oliech restaurant, a popular fish-eating restaurant in Nairobi, is a place they would recommend to anyone visiting the country. '"Africa is the future. We love the beauty of the land and the people, not to mention the countless opportunities. "Anyone who hasn’t been yet is really missing out. There’s truly something for everyone. It’s a chance to connect with cultures and people whose beauty is unimaginable." During the interview, they were asked to recommend where to eat. "Mama Oliech Restaurant in the Kilimani neighbourhood of Nairobi is a must-try. "Order the ugali with fried fish and a side of kachumbari."